⠀⢠⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⠟⠀⠀⠀
⠀⣾⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⣿⡿⠛⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀
⠠⠛⠛⠛⠉⠁⠀⠈⠙⠛⠛⠿⠿⠿⠿⠛⠛⠋⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀
    WHOSINTAPP - WhatsApp OSINT Tool
    """ + Style.RESET_ALL)
    
    # Show legal warning unless skipped
    if not args.no_warning:
        show_legal_warning()
    
    # Get phone number from user or command line
    if args.number:
        phone_input = args.number
    else:
        phone_input = input("\nEnter the phone number (with country code): ").strip()
    
    # Validate phone number
    is_valid, result = validate_phone_number(phone_input)
    if not is_valid:
        print(f"{Fore.RED}Error: {result}{Style.RESET_ALL}")
